fig, ax, hm = heatmap(
    sprinkle(z_temperature)...;
    colormap = :roma,
    colorrange = (-2, 2),
    figure = (; resolution = (800, 400)),
    axis = (; aspect = DataAspect()),
)
Colorbar(fig[:, end + 1], hm)
current_figure()

)
